<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Habitats</h4>
	<div class="text"> Edges of ponds and lakes, basin and sloping fens. Soils can be highly organic. The USFWS Wetland Inventory (1996 national list) recognizes <i>Narthecium californicum</i> and <i>Tofieldia glutinosa</i> as OBL plants. </div>
</div>

        
